data.description: Beautiful 2 flat building fenced in all around.1st floor is a duplex with 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, family room and laundry area. 2nd floor has 2 bedrooms and 1 bath. Hardwood floors in the living room and bedrooms for both units. Kitchens include stainless steel appliances, white cabinets, and granite counters. Beautiful backyard and plenty of parking space in the back. Property close to I-290 and green line. Great opportunity to live in one floor and rent the other unit or rent both units. Sold AS-IS.
